<h3>Comments about the CD</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>&ldquo;&#39;Improvisations From The Other Side&#39; by Diane Willis and John Fish is quite a surprise. I say this because it is so good, so refreshing, so mystical that it ranks way &#39;up there&#39; with the best of Native American flute pieces and talented artists. Diane, I knew you were good but I didn&#39;t know you were THAT good. This is one of my favorite CDs and I play it often. Highly recommended!&rdquo;</p><p>&ndash;<cite>P. M. H. Atwater, L.H.D., NDE Researcher and Author of &ldquo;The New Children and Near-Death Experiences,&rdquo; &ldquo;Beyond the Light,&rdquo; &ldquo;Future Memory,&rdquo; and others.</cite></p></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&ldquo;The whole recording is beautifully played&mdash;and produced! Your improvisational skills are fantastic&hellip;.&rdquo;</p><p>&ndash;<cite>Walfrid Kujala, flute and piccolo, Chicago Symphony Orchestra, 1954-2001; Professor of Flute, Northwestern University, 1962-present.</cite></p></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&ldquo;During our trip to the Yucatan, we enjoyed this CD for its melodic and soothing melodies; we played it continually. It is a must have!!! We think Diane is hot!&rdquo;</p><p>&ndash;<cite>Dannion and Kathryn Brinkley, Near-Death Experiencer; Hospice Volunteer; Author of Saved by the Light and Secrets of the Light</cite></p></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&ldquo;Wow&mdash;it&#39;s beautiful: Congratulations and thanks&hellip;.&rdquo;</p><p>&ndash;<cite>Paula Robison, Concert and Recording Artist, also renowned for her master classes, original transcriptions and books on the art of flute playing.</cite></p></blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>&ldquo;I am just playing your CD and I love it! I picked it up at my office a couple of days ago and I have played it non stop! You and John have done a super job - it is just beautiful&hellip;.it has been so healing and calming for me. Bless you. Best to you and John - what a great duo.&rdquo;</p><p>&ndash;<cite>Caroline Sutherland, Medical Intuitive and Author of &ldquo;The Body Knows.&rdquo; Vancouver, BC, Canada</cite></p></blockquote>
